data.description: IMPROVED PRICING!  Here is the executive home you have been waiting for! Choice Home Warranty included! This spacious and stately home is conveniently located in Holly Springs close to restaurants and shopping. Home features a large open concept kitchen with granite countertops, tile backsplash, built in desk, built in microwave, island and a double oven. Fenced in backyard features great landscaping, a deck and a fire pit that is perfect for entertaining. Third floor features a 5th BR that can also be used large bonus with a built in surround sound system.  And....it has its own en suite bath. New water heater in 2022. Additionally, refrigerator, washer and dryer convey!
